name: Homura
profile:
She seems to be a magical girl, but there are a lot 
of mysteries surrounding the way she acts.

name: Sayaka
profile:
Madoka’s classmate and good friend. Energetic and 
lively.

name: Mami
profile:
A ninth-grader who attends Mitakihara Middle School.
A kind senior to Madoka, she’s the helpful.

name: Kyoko
profile:
A magical girl who simply has supernatural powers and 
abandoned the premise of justice and benevolence.

name: Madoka
profile:
A good-natured and ordinary eighth-grader. 
She is the health coordinator in her class.
